{"tid":1515282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［文宣！］中學生9月3罷課，9月2無聲抗議","createTime":"2019-08-29T05:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:32:27.000Z","uid":167634,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e704892153b5c217aaf1e63cbc76bd64a3e5ef","tid":1515282,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"香港中學生罷課聯盟已經開左記招叫大家9月3罷課<br />\n但大家「開學日」唔係無野做架<br />\n請大家於開學日9月2<br />\n戴上你地嘅豬咀等gear<br />\n或者紗布口罩<br />\n最好以小隊方式返學行動<br />\n <br />\n請同學們運用創意制作文宣，呼籲大家以支體方式作出無聲抗議<br />\n<br />\n中學生，請用呢種方法在開學日作出無聲抗議⋯⋯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496444</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1fea152ede7dbffe3dd3ccbafb31e07de794a24","tid":1515282,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"ea9b3a266d4957b1a3dcc09c6fca0430ec42800c","tid":1515282,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"數字終於郁了<br />\nWhite House Petitions 回來了！可惜反對曾偉雄的聯署過了截止日期一日！令到舊聯署唔到數!<br />\n<br />\n請各兄弟重新簽署以下這個聯署！香港人心不死！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=8bdc16c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition</a>"},{"pid":"a9767ca72caea7c28b58a839273d5240c0bee78b","tid":1515282,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"第9推"},{"pid":"af327bd9058a611019594cdc91bf6adbe1d19187","tid":1515282,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:33